text: Roy Haylock (born June 27, 1975), better known by the stage name Bianca Del Rio, is an American drag queen, comedian, actor, and costume designer. She is known for winning the sixth season of RuPaul's Drag Race. ==References== Category:1975 births Category:Living people Category:American television actors Category:American television personalities Category:American costume designers Category:Actors from New Orleans Category:Comedians from New Orleans Category:Drag queens
